      <p>
        By accessing or using www.obdfaultcode.com, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and our <a href="/en/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>. We may update these terms from time to time; the “Last updated” date at the top of this page will change, and continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
