      </p>

      <h2 id="termination">9. Termination</h2>
      <p>
        We may suspend or discontinue the site or your access at any time, with or without notice, for any reason. Provisions that by their nature should survive (including disclaimers, limitation of liability, and governing law) will remain in effect after termination.
      </p>

